These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Cigar: blend, siglo, fonseca, bongani
Pet: hamster, goldfish, horse, fish
1. Cigar:fonseca is between Pet:horse and Pet:goldfish##2
2. Cigar:bongani is on the left or right of Pet:horse##3
3. Pet:horse is not to the left of Pet:horse##8
4. Pet:goldfish != Cigar:fonseca##6
5. Cigar:fonseca is somewhere to the right of Cigar:blend##5
6. Cigar:blend is on the right of Pet:hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Cigar   | bongani  | blend | fonseca | siglo  |
| Pet   | hamster | horse   | fish  | goldfish |

