.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Birthday: march, october, december, april
Sport: rowing, parkour, climbing, tennis
1. Sport:tennis is not to the left of Sport:tennis##8
2. Birthday:march is somewhere to the right of Birthday:april##5
3. Birthday:march == Sport:parkour##1
4. Birthday:april is between Birthday:march and Birthday:october##2
5. Birthday:october is somewhere between Birthday:december and Sport:rowing##7
6. Sport:climbing is somewhere to the left of Birthday:october##5
7. Sport:rowing is not to the left of Sport:rowing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | december | october          | april | march     |
| Sport    | climbing      | tennis | rowing | parkour |

