3. Hobby:puzzles is on the right of Hobby:card-games##1
4. Hobby:puzzles is in an even position##4
5. Hobby:magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
6. Hobby:card-games is somewhere to the left of Flower:balloon-flower##5
7. Hobby:magic-tricks == Flower:tulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby           | card-games | puzzles | collecting     | magic-tricks |
| Flower   | bellflower    | balloon-flower   | marigold | tulip    |

